<hr />

<h2>Risk vs. Safety</h2>
<table class="table table-bordered">
    <thead class="table-light">
        <tr>
            <th>Good Practice</th>
            <th>Risky Behavior</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        <tr>
            <td>Using two-factor authentication (2FA)</td>
            <td>Same password across sites</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Reviewing app permissions regularly</td>
            <td>Granting full access blindly</td>
        </tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

<hr />

<h2>Simple Privacy Habits</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Use unique, strong passwords</li>
    <li>Enable 2FA on all major accounts</li>
    <li>Review your social media visibility settings</li>
</ul>

